<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;">Transformation is achieved through a fundamental shift in the way you do business. Whether youâ€™re embarking on a transformation due to external market factors or to become more competitive in the marketplace, we have the team to help you get there. Transformation is a long journey and weâ€™re here to support you.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;">Our approach looks at realigning the way your teams' works, how your organisation is structured, the core product or service portfolio of the business and how technology is used. We help you to understand who your stakeholders are and how you should engage them. We help you to agree on the vision of the future state and how it should be delivered.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #333333;">We help you to realise your vision and embed the changes from within so that you can achieve the benefits that you have set for yourself.</span></p>
[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1493776346167{margin-bottom: 34px !important;}"]
<blockquote>
<div data-canvas-width="785.9629788313724"><span style="color: #ffffff;">We ease the pain of change by helping organisations and individuals through the transformation process.</span></div></blockquote>
[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1456219515168{margin-bottom: 27px !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Assessing Impacts" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%23222222" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1493776455833{margin-bottom: 27px !important;}"][stm_charts design="circle" legend_position="right" values_circle="%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22People%22%2C%22value%22%3A%2240%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%238d6dc4%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Process%22%2C%22value%22%3A%2230%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23f79468%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Technology%22%2C%22value%22%3A%2240%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23cec2ab%22%7D%5D" width="208" height="208" css=".vc_custom_1493776567746{margin-bottom: 14px !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 13px; color: #777777; line-height: 22px;">Transforming your business holistically requires assessment of the impacts to your people and teams, how they perform their role today vs in the future and the technology they use.</span></p>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Transformational Success" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%23222222" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1493776674692{margin-bottom: 23px !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<ul>
 	<li><strong>Stakeholder engagement:</strong> Understanding the need to change and gaining consensus</li>
 	<li><strong>Vision:</strong> agreeing what you are looking to achieve, a vision that describes a better future and how to get there</li>
 	<li><strong>Plan:</strong> Understanding what is changing and how to approach the change.</li>
 	<li><strong>Create:</strong> Design the new organisational way of working with supporting structures and technology</li>
 	<li><strong>Go Live:</strong> Implement and continually improve. This is typically done in phases over a number of years.</li>
 	<li><strong>Embed:</strong> Sustain the change to move forward and achieve benefits</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_custom_heading text="Transformation: The Basics" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%23222222" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1493784150794{margin-bottom: 31px !important;}"][vc_tta_accordion shape="square" c_position="right" active_section="1" css=".vc_custom_1456219636222{margin-bottom: 34px !important;}"][vc_tta_section title="Value Creation" tab_id="1452765420119-d4dfaf69-4fae"][vc_column_text]
<div style="text-align: justify;" data-canvas-width="842.4358494043145"><span style="color: #333333;">Focus on the areas where value is created in an organization including top line, bottom line, capital and operating expenditure. We can show you how to streamline and create value.</span></div>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Mindset" tab_id="1493784159821-1e25d2b4-618d"][vc_column_text]
<div style="text-align: justify;" data-canvas-width="833.2886549690197"><span style="color: #333333;">We work closely with leaders to ensure they have the right approach andÂ </span><span style="color: #333333;">mindset to ensure that the changes are adopted and the people areÂ </span><span style="color: #333333;">supported to maximize effectiveness and sustainability of the change.</span></div>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Business Benefits " tab_id="1493784269755-f3c9655e-8245"][vc_column_text]
<div style="text-align: justify;" data-canvas-width="833.2886549690197">
<div style="text-align: justify;" data-canvas-width="813.8009445611763"><span style="color: #333333;">Our qualified team helps you to achieve business benefits by increasing adoption and utilisation of your changes.We do this through engaging all key stakeholders to assist you to design the most effective business processes.</span></div>
</div>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Engaging is Easy" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%23222222" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1493784358546{margin-bottom: 23px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1493780509799{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]
<div style="text-align: justify;" data-canvas-width="328.72024610666665">Not sure where to start? Weâ€™re here to help you through your transformation. These are just a few of the services we can provide:</div>
[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]
<ul>
 	<li><strong>Vision-setting workshops</strong></li>
 	<li><strong>Stakeholder engagement planning</strong></li>
 	<li><strong>Business Benefits definition</strong></li>
 	<li><strong>Organisational Design</strong></li>
 	<li><strong>Current vs Future State mapping</strong></li>
 	<li><strong>Change Management Strategy &amp; Planning</strong></li>
</ul>
